  "segments": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 6.48,
      "text": "In Tirmidhi, an en-nameel in Islam, which is like Allah with the prayer of Ashkas Yunus, there is no Marum.",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "start": 6.48,
      "end": 10.48,
      "text": "Lai Allah Allam Tsubhana's M. is a newborn in Marwarts",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "start": 10.48,
      "end": 13.14,
      "text": "There is only knowledge of ki",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "start": 13.14,
      "end": 15.66,
      "text": "This is Sigi Dulstikhfar",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "start": 15.66,
      "end": 23.1,
      "text": "In this world, I have gone to sing in front of my Lord in a simple way.",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "start": 23.1,
      "end": 25.900000000000002,
      "text": "Lai Allah symbol",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "start": 25.900000000000002,
      "end": 28.3,
      "text": "There is no time to fear Allah",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "start": 29.26,
      "end": 30.98,
      "text": "Glory be to you",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "start": 30.98,
      "end": 33.34,
      "text": "So he will not make a mistake",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "start": 33.34,
      "end": 34.480000000000004,
      "text": "Kani Kalti Marud",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "start": 34.480000000000004,
      "end": 36.92,
      "text": "I will make mistakes, I am human",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "start": 36.92,
      "end": 38.4,
      "text": "So just weave it",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "start": 38.4,
      "end": 41.16,
      "text": "O Allah, he did such a thing",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "start": 41.16,
      "end": 46.68,
      "text": "A shaks on whom is the share of Allah that the Surahs came in Safaat",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "start": 46.68,
      "end": 54.56,
      "text": "That if Yunus had not called us in the belly of the stomach with woolen wool, he would have come out on the day when the dead come out of their graves.",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "start": 54.82,
      "end": 56.56,
      "text": "Those of them",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "start": 56.56,
      "end": 59.56,
      "text": "In this case, it is such a hot time",
      "language": "en",
      "style": "clean"
    }
  ],
